title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Aug 9 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Aug 9 2021
description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 2: Clay and Buck welcome Dr. Marty Makary of Johns Hopkins to the show to discuss mask mandates for children. Is natural immunity better than vaccine immunity? Will Governor Cuomo, go? Defund the police has consequences. Another bloody weekend in Chicago, 13 killed, 86 shot over weekend.
